Welcome to MIUI Notes!

Now you can easily and conveniently jot down ideas, memos, thoughts using.

Attach pictures or contacts:
☺ %s

Check of tasks with your finger:
☺ %s

And more great features:

  - Sort by dragging
  - Set reminders
  - Export to SD card

